CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 31, 1955, pg. B4, reads: "The Christmas Spirit - Mrs. Julia B. Gaines, owner of the Gaines Funeral Funeral [sic] Home in East Liberty, displays the Christmas spirit as she gives a youngster a box of Christmas goodies as others wait in line. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Julia B. Gaines, handing out Christmas goodies to boys and girls waiting in line, for Gaines Funeral Home Christmas party, East Liberty
